Text: Where do I enter the key?I loaded the program, it says 21 days left on trial where do I go to enter the key?

It should be a registry key 

just double click it...........or open regedit and import the file 
to do this click start......click on run.....then type regedit .....then click ok

If your running win 7 just type it in search box 

when regedit opens click on file then import.....and import the key file
